[[File:DarkwalkerUnderlord-TPOV.jpg|thumb|right|250px|A [[Rodian/Legends|Rodian]] [[Darkwalkers|Darkwalker]] Underlord]]
'''Underlord''' was the highest title for [[Black Sun/Legends|Black Sun]] leaders. [[Dal Perhi]] was Underlord and later [[Prince/Legends|Prince]] [[Xizor/Legends|Xizor]], when he won this title during competition with [[Kaird]], though he was more commonly known as the [[Dark Prince]]. "Underlord" may also have been the title given to all leaders of the criminal syndicate.

Underlord was also a title of the highest rank within the [[Darkwalkers]] criminal organization on [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]].

